data.description: This  is an entertainers’ paradise, in the much sought after Downingtown Area School District. This 6 bedroom, 4 full and 2 half bath house in the desirable Marshall Creek Farm neighborhood is situated on a 3-acre corner lot. The uniqueness of every house in Marshall Creek Farms & large lots makes this a very special place to live .What sets this house apart from all the others is the spacious private outdoor pool area, complete with covered patio, outdoor fireplace, hot tub, and built in stainless steel grill with ceramic plates. In addition, a full tennis court with lights has been converted to a sport court with artificial turf and a basketball backboard. You will enjoy evenings under the lights, or if preferred, restore the tennis court to its former glory.The gourmet kitchen includes high end Viking stove top and griddle, as well as dual Viking ovens, and two Thermador warming drawers. The custom maple cabinets are by Honey Brook Custom Cabinets and feature an oversized built-in pantry and built in Gaggenau coffee machine. The first-floor open plan features hickory floors and multi-level family room windows that overlook the pool area. Rounding out the main floor includes a formal dining room, office and guest bedroom and bath. The primary bedroom features two closets and a primary bathroom with heated tile floor and an oversized shower with dual shower heads and a heated natural river stone floor. Bedrooms two, three, and four share a hall bathroom, while the fifth bedroom has an in-suite bathroom.The finished walkout basement includes a workout room, or second office, as well as a second kitchen, complete with refrigerator/freezer, sink, and dishwasher. The basement kitchen in invaluable for entertaining, as it is the perfect setup to host your outdoor parties. This house has been upgraded to include a backup generator with 1,500-gallon propane tanks and two zone geothermal units with a backup hydronic boiler. The salt water pool had new mechanicals including a new liner in 2022, and all new electronics and chlorinator in 2023. There is also an electric car hook up.
